```txt
# .gameAgent
# Svarga Dimsum Memory Card Event System
# Secure Architecture Rules
# Next.js + Vercel + Google Apps Script + Google Spreadsheet

#################################################
# CORE SYSTEM PRINCIPLE
#################################################

This system is:
- frontend game + protected backend
- NOT public spreadsheet architecture
- NOT direct Apps Script architecture

Main priority:
1. Voucher security
2. Apps Script secrecy
3. Fair winner system
4. Anti-cheat
5. Spam protection

#################################################
# FINAL SYSTEM FLOW
#################################################

User
↓
Frontend Game (Next.js)
↓
Internal API Route (/api/game)
↓
Google Apps Script
↓
Google Spreadsheet

STRICT RULE:
Frontend MUST NEVER directly communicate with:
- Spreadsheet
- Apps Script URL

#################################################
# GAME CONCEPT
#################################################

Game type:
- Memory Card Match

Rules:
- 30 seconds timer
- 3 lives
- wrong match closes card
- all cards matched = win

Reward:
- voucher code

Redeem:
- directly at store
OR
- send voucher code to WhatsApp admin

#################################################
# DAILY WINNER SYSTEM
#################################################

Only 1 winner per day allowed.

Flow:
- game opens at 13:00 WIB
- first valid winner gets voucher
- game instantly closes
- all other players rejected

Frontend MUST show:
🏆 Pemenang Hari Ini

Required:
- winner name
- winning time

Forbidden:
- exposing full phone numbers
- exposing private data

#################################################
# REQUIRED FORM
#################################################

Before game starts:
user MUST input:

Required:
- nama
- whatsapp

Optional:
- kota
- instagram

Validation:
- whatsapp unique per day
- no empty fields
- sanitize input

#################################################
# GAME VALIDATION RULES
#################################################

Backend MUST validate:
- current game hour
- existing winner
- duplicate players
- fake requests
- impossible completion time

Frontend MUST NOT:
- generate voucher
- decide winner
- store voucher list
- validate reward

#################################################
# GAME SCHEDULE
#################################################

Timezone:
Asia/Jakarta

Open:
13:00 WIB

Close:
17:00 WIB
OR instantly after winner exists

Backend MUST validate schedule.

Frontend-only validation is forbidden.

#################################################
# REQUIRED ARCHITECTURE
#################################################

Allowed:

Frontend
↓
Next.js API Route
↓
Apps Script
↓
Spreadsheet

Forbidden:
❌ Frontend -> Apps Script
❌ Frontend -> Spreadsheet

#################################################
# APPS SCRIPT SECURITY
#################################################

Apps Script URL is SECRET.

STRICT RULES:
- NEVER expose Apps Script URL in frontend
- NEVER use NEXT_PUBLIC for Apps Script
- NEVER hardcode Apps Script URL in client components
- NEVER call Apps Script directly from browser

Apps Script URL MUST only exist in:
.env.local

Correct:

GAME_API_URL=https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbzda_0Oar-IEl6p0CdAQ2X9jIxncf7YGn0fHJO9LHYEWDD_oENsrTuPmklDMF-G0AcJ/exec

GAME_SECRET=svarga_secret_2026

Forbidden:
NEXT_PUBLIC_GAME_API_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_GAME_SECRET=

#################################################
# SPREADSHEET SECURITY
#################################################

Spreadsheet MUST:
- remain private
- NEVER be public
- NEVER use "Anyone with link"

Allowed access:
- owner only

Apps Script executes as:
- owner account only

Spreadsheet ID MUST NEVER:
- appear in frontend
- appear in browser network tab
- appear in public repo
- appear in client-side code

#################################################
# ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
#################################################

Required:

.env.local

Variables:
GAME_API_URL=
GAME_SECRET=
ADMIN_WHATSAPP=

Forbidden:
NEXT_PUBLIC_GAME_API_URL
NEXT_PUBLIC_GAME_SECRET

Secrets MUST stay server-side only.

#################################################
# NEXT.JS API SECURITY
#################################################

Frontend communicates ONLY with:

/api/game

Internal route responsibilities:
- forward request to Apps Script
- inject secret
- sanitize payload
- validate request

Apps Script MUST reject requests without secret.

#################################################
# REQUIRED API ROUTES
#################################################

/api/game/status
/api/game/start
/api/game/finish
/api/game/winner

Frontend MUST NOT know:
- Apps Script endpoints
- Spreadsheet structure
- Voucher pool

#################################################
# ANTI-CHEAT RULES
#################################################

Backend MUST reject:
- repeated finish requests
- impossible solve duration
- manipulated payloads
- duplicate WhatsApp
- multiple wins

Recommended:
- signed session tokens
- timestamp validation
- cooldown logic

#################################################
# RATE LIMITING
#################################################

Per WhatsApp:
- 1 play/day

Per IP:
- max 5 requests/day

Required:
- reject spam
- reject brute force
- log suspicious requests

#################################################
# VOUCHER SECURITY
#################################################

Voucher format:
SVRGA-XXXX-XXXX

Voucher states:
- unused
- used

On claim:
- instantly mark used
- save winner data

Forbidden:
- predictable sequences
- frontend voucher generation
- exposing voucher list

#################################################
# REQUIRED SPREADSHEET STRUCTURE
#################################################

Required sheets:
- players
- vouchers
- daily_winner
- settings
- logs

#################################################
# SHEET: players
#################################################

Columns:
| id |
| nama |
| whatsapp |
| ip |
| status |
| play_date |
| created_at |

status:
- win
- lose

#################################################
# SHEET: vouchers
#################################################

Columns:
| code |
| status |
| claimed_by |
| claimed_at |
| player_ip |

status:
- unused
- used

#################################################
# SHEET: daily_winner
#################################################

Columns:
| tanggal |
| nama |
| whatsapp |
| voucher |
| waktu_menang |

STRICT RULE:
Only 1 row per day allowed.

#################################################
# SHEET: settings
#################################################

Columns:
| key |
| value |

Default values:
| game_open | true |
| start_hour | 13 |
| end_hour | 17 |

#################################################
# SHEET: logs
#################################################

Columns:
| type |
| message |
| ip |
| created_at |

Required logs:
- spam attempts
- duplicate plays
- invalid requests
- fake finish attempts

#################################################
# FRONTEND REQUIREMENTS
#################################################

Required UI:
- memory cards
- countdown timer
- lives counter
- winner popup
- game closed state
- daily winner section

Required messages:
- already played
- game closed
- winner exists
- victory
- defeat

#################################################
# DEPLOYMENT RULES
#################################################

Hosting:
- Vercel

Production requirements:
- HTTPS only
- environment variables enabled
- source maps disabled
- remove debug logs

#################################################
# SEO & INDEXING SECURITY
#################################################

Sensitive backend endpoints MUST NOT be indexed.

Required:
robots.txt

Rules:

User-agent: *
Disallow: /api/
Disallow: /admin/

Required headers:

X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow

Apps Script URL MUST NEVER:
- appear in HTML
- appear in metadata
- appear in sitemap
- appear in robots
- appear in frontend requests

#################################################
# GIT SECURITY
#################################################

Required:
.gitignore

Must ignore:
.env
.env.local
.env.production

Forbidden:
- pushing secrets to GitHub
- exposing Spreadsheet ID publicly
- committing Apps Script URLs

#################################################
# FINAL DEVELOPMENT PRINCIPLE
#################################################

System philosophy:
- simple
- secure
- maintainable
- server-controlled

Avoid:
- overengineering
- frontend trust
- public backend exposure

Because the moment a random teenager discovers browser DevTools, they immediately transform into a self-proclaimed cybersecurity specialist with unlimited free time.
```
